##### MF3: REACTION CROSS SECTIONS                                7728 1451
                                                                  7728 1451
All the data present in the following MT-sections have been       7728 1451
calculated with TALYS, possibly normalized to experimental data.  7728 1451
If the maximal cross section in an excitation function over the   7728 1451
whole energy range does not exceed 1.e-9 b, the MT-number is not  7728 1451
included. Cross sections lower than 1.e-20 b are assumed to have  7728 1451
no physical meaning and are set to zero. All MT numbers extend up 7728 1451
to the highest incident energy.                                   7728 1451
The following reaction channels/MT numbers are generally included:7728 1451
                                                                  7728 1451
- MT1      : Total cross section                                  7728 1451
                                                                  7728 1451
Calculated with the optical model over the whole energy range,    7728 1451
or partly reproduced using experimental data.                     7728 1451
                                                                  7728 1451
- MT2      : Elastic scattering cross section                     7728 1451
                                                                  7728 1451
Obtained by subtracting the non-elastic cross section from the    7728 1451
total cross section.                                              7728 1451
                                                                  7728 1451
- MT3      : Non-elastic cross section                            7728 1451
                                                                  7728 1451
Calculated with the optical model over the whole energy range.    7728 1451
                                                                  7728 1451
- MT4      : Total inelastic cross section                        7728 1451
                                                                  7728 1451
Sum of MT=51-91.                                                  7728 1451
                                                                  7728 1451
- MT5      : (n,anything) cross section                           7728 1451
                                                                  7728 1451
MT5 contains the reactions which can not be stored in any other   7728 1451
MT-number. The information of MF3/MT5 can be combined with        7728 1451
MF6/MT5 to obtain residual production cross sections particle     7728 1451
production cross sections and (double-)differential cross         7728 1451
sections.                                                         7728 1451
